    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a solid car for me. It\u2019s in really great shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect if you're looking for a reliable daily driver that's been well-loved and looked after. It\u2019s ready for a new home and many more road trips! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
