    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun? This beauty has been well-loved and is still running like a dream. It\u2019s in great shape, super clean inside and out, and honestly just a blast to drive. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, it\u2019s ready for any adventure you throw at it. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
