    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently serviced for optimal cam timing. The power is managed by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional traction and mechanical grip. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to handle the chassis's torsional loads, and the suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers to maintain the platform's legendary poise. While the vehicle shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved performance car, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a visceral driving experience with precise turn-in and a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
